    <title>CKAN: Ticket #331: Timezone of CKAN timestamps should be configurable</title>
    <link>http://localhost/ticket/331</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;
Would like to set timezone for a CKAN instance to use in rendering timestamps. For example, use CET or EST timezone.
&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
